      "score": 205,
      "comments": 100,
      "author": "soheilpro",
      "published": "2026-07-15T10:06:39Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Deploy Telegram bots on scale-to-zero runtimes like Cloudflare Workers or AWS Lambda to eliminate idle VM costs.",
        "Transition from polling to webhooks to trigger serverless executions, reducing API overhead and latency for ChatOps workflows.",
        "Store ephemeral session state in lightweight external stores like Cloudflare KV or DynamoDB to maintain stateless, fast-booting functions."
      ]
    },
